description: Our Organic Pineapple Juice is made from ripe, organically grown pineapples, offering a refreshing and tropical taste. It's packed with vitamins and minerals, making it a healthy and delicious choice for any time of day.

Freshly squeezed from organically grown oranges, our Organic Orange Juice is bursting with flavor and packed with vitamin C. It's a classic breakfast staple, perfect for starting your day on a bright note.
Our Organic Apple Juice is made from the juiciest, organically grown apples, providing a crisp and refreshing taste. Naturally sweet and enjoyable, it's a great hydrating option for all ages.

Extracted from premium, organically grown cranberries, our Organic Cranberry Juice is tart and invigorating. It's not only delicious but also known for its health benefits, including urinary tract health support.

Rich in flavor and antioxidants, our Organic Purple Grape Juice is made from carefully selected, organically grown purple grapes. This heart-healthy juice is both nutritious and delicious, making it an excellent choice for any time of day.

Squeezed from ripe organic pink grapefruits, our Pink Grapefruit Juice offers a perfect balance of tartness and sweetness. Loaded with vitamin C, it's a refreshing and invigorating choice that's ideal for kickstarting your mornings or as a pick-me-up during the day.
Our Organic Spaghetti is a classic pasta made from the finest organic durum wheat semolina. Perfect for traditional Italian dishes, it offers a delightful texture and taste.

Our Whole Wheat Fusilli is made from 100% whole grain durum wheat, providing a healthier alternative with a nutty flavor and excellent texture. Ideal for holding onto sauces and making your dishes more nutritious.

Our Organic Penne Rigate is made from high-quality organic semolina, offering a ridged texture that's perfect for catching every type of sauce. It's a versatile pasta that complements a wide range of dishes.

Our Organic Tagliatelle is crafted from the finest organic durum wheat, creating wide, flat noodles that are ideal for rich and creamy sauces. Each batch is extruded through traditional bronze dies for perfect texture.

Our Whole Wheat Spaghetti offers all the nutritional benefits of whole grains in a classic pasta shape. Its robust flavor and excellent texture make it a great foundation for any sauce, from traditional marinara to light olive oil-based dressings.

Our Organic Linguine is a traditional Italian pasta, slightly flatter than spaghetti and perfect for seafood dishes. Made from organic durum wheat semolina, it provides a delightful base for your favorite pasta recipes.

Our Whole Wheat Rigatoni has a delightful texture and nutty flavor, making it perfect for robust sauces. Made from 100% whole grain durum wheat, it's a healthier option that doesn't compromise on taste or quality.

Also known as 'bow-tie pasta,' our Organic Farfalle is perfect for cold pasta salads or serving with creamy sauces. Made from the finest organic durum wheat, it's a fun and versatile pasta shape that's sure to please.
Our Organic Basmati White Rice is aromatic and long-grained, perfect for a variety of dishes from curries to pilafs. Grown organically, it offers a fragrant aroma and a fluffy texture when cooked.

Packed with natural nutrients and fiber, our Whole Grain Brown Rice is a healthy and versatile staple for any meal. Its nutty flavor and chewy texture make it a perfect base for stir-fries, salads, and pilafs.

Our Organic Jasmine White Rice is known for its fragrant aroma and delicate floral notes. It cooks up soft and sticky, making it an excellent choice for Asian dishes, including Thai curries and Vietnamese stir-fries.
Our Organic Basmati White Rice is aromatic and long-grained, perfect for a variety of dishes from curries to pilafs. Grown organically, it offers a fragrant aroma and a fluffy texture when cooked.

Our Long Life Whole Milk is gently processed to preserve its rich and creamy taste. With all the goodness of fresh milk, it's perfect for your daily dairy needs, offering convenience without compromising on flavor or nutrition.

Enjoy the perfect balance of taste and low fat with our Long Life Semi-Skimmed Milk. It's ideal for those who prefer a lighter option but still enjoy the creamy taste of milk in their coffee, tea, cereals, or cooking.

Our Long Life Skimmed Milk is the lightest option in our dairy range, perfect for those monitoring their calorie intake. It retains the essential nutrients of milk while being low in fat, making it a healthy choice for the whole family.

Our Organic Greek Yogurt is thick, creamy, and rich in protein. With no added sugar, it's an excellent choice for those managing diabetes. Enjoy its tangy taste plain or with your favorite low-glycemic toppings.
ingredients: Organic Skimmed Milk, Live Active Cultures

description: Infused with natural vanilla extract, our Low-Fat Vanilla Yogurt combines the creamy texture of yogurt with the sweet, comforting taste of vanilla. While lower in fat, it contains added sugars, making it less suitable for those with diabetes.
ingredients: Skimmed Milk, Sugar, Natural Vanilla Flavor, Live Active Cultures

description: Inspired by Icelandic tradition, our High-Protein Skyr Yogurt is made from skimmed milk, resulting in a high-protein, low-fat yogurt with no added sugar. Its thick texture and mild taste make it suitable for diabetes-friendly diets.

ingredients: Milk, Strawberries, Sugar, Natural Flavors, Live Active Cultures
